      "id": "PopularPost183674",
      "post_content": "@statiefreez  \n  \nI agree with infernox, this is not SO much better than [Lave Axe](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lave Axe) in ANY situation. If I used this to target someone's head, durring my main phase, and they have 5 life both cards have the same function, and lava axe is very slightly easier to cast. At the very least this is only a bit better than [Lava Axe](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lava Axe) in several situation.  \n  \nAs infernox said, better than [Lava Axe](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lava Axe) in most situations, but once in a blue moon you may see this in your hand in a multi colour deck, and wish that you had [Lava Axe](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lava Axe) because your mountains are in your deck/destroyed.",
      "posted_by": "whiteshadw",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost183674\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_post\">@statiefreez<br/><br/>I agree with infernox, this is not SO much better than <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Lave Axe\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lave Axe\">Lave Axe</a> in ANY situation.  If I used this to target someone's head, durring my main phase, and they have 5 life both cards have the same function, and lava axe is very slightly easier to cast.  At the very least this is only a bit better than <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Lava Axe\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lava Axe\">Lava Axe</a> in several situation.<br/><br/>As infernox said, better than <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Lava Axe\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lava Axe\">Lava Axe</a> in most situations, but once in a blue moon you may see this in your hand in a multi colour deck, and wish that you had <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Lava Axe\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lava Axe\">Lava Axe</a> because your mountains are in your deck/destroyed.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '183674'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy50322\">whiteshadw</span>\r\n                                (7/30/2011 3:22:37 PM)\r\n    